Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,请便
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你们准备一个轮椅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 立刻准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,睡个好觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不过睡得还凑合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏你们 我睡得很香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来母亲的仪式好像要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,大家也会去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,尚城不拒绝任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,无论何人都会给予他生活的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样一个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是为了让大家开心才被呼唤来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,吃惊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,大家可以自由参加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是宗教吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:03:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的人都是被母亲的能力吸引过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,聚集在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人就是母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来将要举行和死者的会面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,死者?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲她可以与死人对话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么胡话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我没骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.47,0:03:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能 这太扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有母亲那种能力的人被称为灵媒师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,灵媒师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,指的是死后世界与现世之间的媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就是半熟和全熟的中间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,被选中的参加者请到颜之间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,去跟上那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 刚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,想看仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是用金继
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是为了复原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,注入新的生命让它延续
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,才是我们的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,死者的仪式也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,死者无法复活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可是知晓死者想法的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可以借助大地大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,与死者连接并使对话成立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,然后幸存者将开始新的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这股气味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,大麻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:04:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那是大地大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,尚城的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,以大地大人作为媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可以让母亲使用出能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,难道10岁的是他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不久将举办诞生10周年的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,佳惠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你救了被海啸卷走的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,密码就在金库的里面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,替我活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我会一直守护着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这是父亲的钟表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真也 喂 真也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听到我说的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在倒塌的屋子里我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,丢下我自己跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要是连你也死掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,像大峡谷一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这是琵琶湖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,湖底出现了一条巨大的裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,水就流了进去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多的水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想和爸爸说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,总之就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我认为不是谁都能够参加仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这里能够看到菲律宾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,开个玩笑 吓到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,才不会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 你也笑起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,大家来拍张照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那个仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么做才能被选上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,根据天启
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,请勿靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,信不信是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是某个男子的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你摸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,想要与死者见面请根据顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我在和母亲讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲一天只能会见三人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,想休息的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女孩是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是七海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,刚 全部吃掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我会吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是哪里的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,南斯拉夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候经常吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:08:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,多吃点多吃点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这是科索沃的名菜炖肉汤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnAvenir Next W1G\b1\pos(793,668)}Paçe
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,新来的 来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,偏食对健康不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不想被胖子说健康问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,吃了饭就去上学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有哦 虽然也就几十人左右
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,刚 步 今天开始去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大家要是想工作的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,也尽管说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,还有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在三角形abc中 边bc为底边时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,顶点a到底边bc的垂线长度为三角形的高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好多大麻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,工作真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛很痒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,地震?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你是知道地震会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能 不会这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,学校如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,日本人太多了很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,挑三拣四可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,力士什锦火锅 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,力士吃的那个东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你喜欢相扑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没兴趣 大谷先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我是非常喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我能成为职业力士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 只是身体大是赢不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,刚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,和爸爸对话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,摩尔斯电码 随便做了下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸绝对看得见的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,想听爸爸的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不行?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕爸爸会胡言乱语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还有可能生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 反正你也猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,火好像熄灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我去借个打火机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我心中的阴霾已经不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是也要参加比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人都在说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,要去派对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,据说是周末的派对 在今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我被邀请过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,已经熄灭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,换你来吹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 着起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是没熄灭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,头发长长了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 妈妈你不去派对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不习惯去吵闹的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是很想听爸爸的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈不想听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不想听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因为没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,其实你是想和那个人搞好关系的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你想忘记关于爸爸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,步 请你懂事点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我就是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙和前辈也在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有不去派对的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,明明派对那么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔也让自己休息下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax Relax
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你最想见的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 其实是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,吵架可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我能好好和她说就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,筋疲力尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,让自己稍微放松下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要是不撑着我就要崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就是这样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也正处于这种时期
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你的家乡是南斯拉夫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我的国家和家庭都已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我还有这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也还在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,托你的福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是我录的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 好好看好好听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我是DJ KITE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别擅自用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的唱片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,让作者来搓碟更好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不能播放的唱片就只是个圆盘而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,DJ春生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,春生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没有退路了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,再不开始观众就要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,解放自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,日本最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,静候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,去那边聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,已经接受母亲的仪式了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我这里有个可以插队的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,和我亲热起来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我这里有后门可以让你走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这种就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不会弄疼你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,保证让你舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,神奇女侠一击就打倒了攻击地球的异形
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到你吸了大麻会变成那种小屁孩性格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,异形是啥来着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不立刻离开日本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那些有钱人好像都想逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因为很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,即使失去了重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有时间伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这太残酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,悲伤也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这样爸爸会生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,擦干眼泪前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸经常说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,正因为有连自己的国家和家庭都回不去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才得忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我以后再也不会哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.87,0:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要动 举起手来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,看样子不是为了通知面会的时间而来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,果然在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,爷爷来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.75,0:23:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,药 药
